Package: mvMixDist
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2019-01-22
Title: mvMixDist: Sampling and Fitting of Multivariate Mixture Distributions
Authors@R: c(person("Georg", "Schnabel", role = c("aut", "cre"),
		     email = "georg.schnabel@nucleardata.com"))
Author: Georg Schnabel [aut, cre],
Maintainer: Georg Schnabel <georg.schnabel@nucleardata.com>
Depends:
    R (>= 3.1.0)
Description: This package implements multivariate distributions and
    mixtures thereof as S4 classes. Functions are provided to 
    query probability densities, sample from distributions, and
    estimate distributions parameters either via the EM algorithm
    or Gibbs sampling.
License: GPL (>= 3)
URL: https://www.r-project.org, https://github.com/gschnabel/mvMixDist
BugReports: https://github.com/gschnabel/mvMixDist/issues
RoxygenNote: 6.1.1
Collate: 
  'dist_generic.R'
  'dist_mixture.R'
  'dist_mvn.R'
  'dist_constant.R'
  'distributions.R'
